### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Low-risk transaction -> allow
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "txn_id": "TXN-DEMO-001",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-25T10:15:00Z",
  "amount_kobo": 1500000,
  "channel": "mobile",
  "sender_account": "0123456789",
  "beneficiary_account": "9876543210",
  "beneficiary_bank_code": "058",
  "device_id": "dev-001",
  "ip_address": "102.89.1.1",
  "geo_state": "Lagos",
  "is_new_beneficiary": false,
  "sender_kyc_tier": 2
}

### Mark a known mule
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/feedback/mule?account=1111111111

### High-risk transfer to known mule -> block
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "txn_id": "TXN-DEMO-002",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-25T02:30:00Z",
  "amount_kobo": 500000000,
  "channel": "mobile",
  "sender_account": "0987654321",
  "beneficiary_account": "1111111111",
  "beneficiary_bank_code": "058",
  "device_id": "dev-002",
  "geo_state": "Lagos",
  "is_new_beneficiary": true,
  "sender_kyc_tier": 1
}

### Submit fraud confirmation
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "txn_id": "TXN-DEMO-002",
  "is_fraud": true,
  "fraud_type": "account_takeover",
  "notes": "Customer reported unauthorised drain via SIM swap"
}
